{\an5}I've improved the jutsu
technique by adjusting
it to my chakra. It'll
be easier to control now.

267
00:20:42,557 --> 00:20:47,097
{\an4}And also, I need to
test situations
involving intent and
memory.

268
00:20:52,204 --> 00:20:54,274
{\an1}<i>You still don't</i>
<i>have enough?</i>

269
00:20:55,041 --> 00:20:57,344
Am I supposed to
go looking for it?

270
00:20:59,213 --> 00:21:02,784
{\an1}Well, you certainly
like putting me to
work, don't you?

271
00:21:03,019 --> 00:21:07,090
{\an1}But that's fine by me.
It's something to look
forward to.

272
00:21:09,327 --> 00:21:11,863
{\an1}Naruto, of course.

273
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:55,270
{\an1}<i>I wish I could</i>
<i>see them!</i>

274
00:22:55,303 --> 00:22:57,172
<i>Mama! Papa!</i>

275
00:22:57,205 --> 00:23:00,810
{\an1}<i>I can't stand how</i>
<i>much I miss them!</i>

276
00:23:01,845 --> 00:23:03,180
<i>(crying)</i>

277
00:23:03,213 --> 00:23:04,749
<i>Why are you</i>
<i>so lonely?</i>

278
00:23:04,782 --> 00:23:05,817
{\an1}<i>Huh?</i>

279
00:23:05,850 --> 00:23:07,753
<i>Look, you're</i>
<i>not alone.</i>

